reviewText: The one star is for the seller and the OBVIOUSLY paid great/5 star feedback.  For $25 I want to know what is this about?  I know of Mr. Buchanan and Controlled Remote Viewing. I was hoping there would be DVDs of his as I seriously want to learn......but you don't describe what's on the DVD....at all.  Controlled Remote Influencing....sparked my interests but seriously? No description?
